headline: This Week In Digital Payment - Fiserv's Strategic Growth Amidst Digital Payments Evolution
summary: Recent developments in the digital payment sector highlight the evolving landscape of financial services technology. Fiserv, a leader in payments and financial technology solutions, has reported its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year of 2025, showcasing modest revenue growth amid mixed performance across different segments. The company achieved a 4% increase in GAAP revenue for the year, driven by growth in its Merchant Solutions. Despite challenges, Fiserv continues to...

headline: Companies Are Replacing CEOs in Record Numbers—and They’re Getting Younger
summary: There hasn’t been such a big crop of new leaders running Corporate America in at least 16 years, and they have their hands full.
